---
title: Smart Moroccan Braised Chicken with Roasted Pepper-Spinach Couscous
description: Sweet and fruity fig spread is the secret ingredient in this quick Moroccan-spiced chicken braise served atop roasted pepper and spinach couscous!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/poulet-braise-a-la-marocaine-98546a63.jpg
